1404	Stimulus Funds Premium Pork?	stimulus-funds-premium-pork	2	"I'm assuming that either there's an error somewhere, or this is really, really good ham. From Recovery.gov's new recipient data comes <a href=""http://www.recovery.gov/?q=content/contracts-recipient-summary&id=12-AG3J14120297196&primeid=27"">this contract</a>, which if I'm reading it right, spends $1,191,200 for ""2 POUND FROZEN HAM SLICED."" 

