180	Following Hastert Through the Revolving Door	following-hastert-through-the-revolving-door	3	"Former House Speaker Dennis Hastert's days raising money for his political campaigns might come in handy when he sits down with the clients of his new employer, law and lobbying firm Dickstein  Shapiro LLP.

