-wave-hits-lehman-wachovia-schwab-and-td-ameritrade/"">sued</a> over its subprime securities), Lehman Brothers (<a herf=""http://www.fosters.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080923/NEWS10/709231689"">which failed</a>) and Bear Stearns (""<a href=""http://ml-implode.com/imploded/lender_BearStearnsResidentialMortgage_2008-03-16.html"">Bear Stearns's mortgage business, a big driver of profits, has been eviscerated</a>,"").

