729	World Bank says protection on the rise	world-bank-says-protection-on-the-rise	2	"<img src=""http://assets.sunlightfoundation.com/projects/tariffdb/tariff_suspensions.png"" style=""vertical-align:text-top; float:right;"" border=""0"">
