<blockquote>We are still waiting for agencies to begin acting on the proactive disclosure elements of the FOIA guidelines.  One of the Holder memo directions was to Ã¢â‚¬Å“not wait for specific requests from the publicÃ¢â‚¬Â but to act in advance of public requests in releasing information.  The recently released OIP guidance goes further to suggest that agencies implement systems to routinely identify and systematically post such information.</blockquote>

