<blockquote>Blank Rome Government Relations professionals and members of the Employment, Benefits and Labor group are monitoring developments on this issue closely.  We are available to assist both existing and potential clients with an understanding as to how the Employee Free Choice Act may affect your company and its business objectives.</blockquote>

